:"68a3531678770ca9419f33cf8ae2f84fe51185d4","tid":144591,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:04:44.000Z","msg":"2 皮野屋企都拎唔到出黎 呢你下半世都幾難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d48cc9e87a3acd7a1dc385ec26655690112543b","tid":144591,"uid":62591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2016-2017個loan申請左，中間好多野補交又呢樣嗰樣，結果到依家要交學費(已經defer左)，佢地仲批緊，仲未有錢到手，點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有個fd拖到近排先搞資助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後聽佢講學資處批左，係唔知全定半額同幾時出<br />\n詳細唔想講，廢事比佢睇到<br />\n雖然唔知佢有冇上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都好啲，因為其實補交資料自己都拖左好耐，好怕學資處話太耐唔批，雖然遲但一定要批啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  第一期學費已經係問親戚借錢黎交，唔批無錢還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f45788001f545c34da2ca3680835e32b13f3880","tid":144591,"uid":62591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2 皮野屋企都拎唔到出黎 呢你下半世都幾難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，不要再說了，老豆過左身，老母係病態賭徒，一直瞞住我賭到屋企一個仙都無剩先我講，嗰陣我仲DSE緊唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"47b9977972621f6d4101ec06c6eb920003ec10ab","tid":144591,"uid":44010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2 皮野屋企都拎唔到出黎 呢你下半世都幾難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，不要再說了，老豆過左身，老母係病態賭徒，一直瞞住我賭到屋企一個仙都無剩先我講，嗰陣我仲DSE緊唔知發生咩事</blockquote><br />\n我屋企都好多野煩<br />\n面家諗緊仲讀唔讀埋落去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274a35f267f5308223193421baebe92e93092ce0","tid":144591,"uid":62591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2 皮野屋企都拎唔到出黎 呢你下半世都幾難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，不要再說了，老豆過左身，老母係病態賭徒，一直瞞住我賭到屋企一個仙都無剩先我講，嗰陣我仲DSE緊唔知發生咩事</blockquote><br />\n我屋企都好多野煩<br />\n面家諗緊仲讀唔讀埋落去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗，自己都想同自己講句無錢就咪學人讀書<br />\n但又唔想就咁放棄，所以真係r爆頭"},{"pid":"22e76bbe6f293345daa2c407c7310253606ef2d0","tid":144591,"uid":44010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2 皮野屋企都拎唔到出黎 呢你下半世都幾難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，不要再說了，老豆過左身，老母係病態賭徒，一直瞞住我賭到屋企一個仙都無剩先我講，嗰陣我仲DSE緊唔知發生咩事</blockquote><br />\n我屋企都好多野煩<br />\n面家諗緊仲讀唔讀埋落去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗，自己都想同自己講句無錢就咪學人讀書<br />\n但又唔想就咁放棄，所以真係r爆頭</blockquote><br />\n你成績好唔好？<br />\n好既緊係繼續讀落去<br />\n我啲成績就麻麻，黎緊要retake一科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nps好彩全班都有2/3要retake呢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}